channel.title: Delta Client[V1] - Old Gameframe, Fixed Models+Cache, More Space, AND MUCH MORE
channel.description:
[size=18pt][b]EDIT: August 19, 2013; Link is dead, however if people will use this I will remake this. It's fairly simple so it's not a problem for me. Shoot me a PM if you would like me too, and when I reach over 10 messages I will. [/b][/size] [b][u][i]Delta Client - Old School Style[/i][/u][/b] This is probably my first release ever, I haven't worked on it much, I just didn't have anything to do today, so I told myself to clean out a Delta client, and I did. Because Delta's are so popular, there are many Delta clients, with half assed sprites on them.. I don't like the sprites on them, so I got back the old gameframe. [b]This is based off of Dragon History V4 Client.[/b] [b]Note: REMEMBER I ONLY WORKED ON THIS FOR BEARLY A DAY, EXPECT MUCH MORE IN [V2]! [/b][b]Note: REMEMBER I ONLY WORKED ON THIS FOR BEARLY A DAY, EXPECT MUCH MORE IN [V2]! [/b]
[i][b][u]Features[/u][/b][/i] [b]-Brung back old RuneScape gameframe 99.99%![/b] -Faster loading up, removed all but 5 images in the Sprites folder -Added a midiplayer, when you start up client, it starts the RuneScape original song. [b]-Cleaned out 5MB. I got rid of un-needed space in the Lunar folder, Sprite folder, and models folder.[/b] [b]-Fresh Clean Cache added. No more floating helmets or messed up fences..[/b] -Fixed a few bugs, like "+++ has logged in/out", never displayed "has logged out", just "in". -Fixed the invisible IP slot on start-up so you only go to Signer ID and ID Pass. -Everything else a Delta client normally has in it.
Note: The only thing that bothers me is that the magic book spell icon is about a pixel off to the left, quick fix if you know what you're doing though.
Tutorial on fixing Magic Icon position: Open up client.java, search for: [code]aClass30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1Array947[6].method348(213, 16083, 14);[/code]
Replace that with this: [code]aClass30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1Array947[6].method348(208, 16083, 14);[/code]
[u][i][b]Images[/b][/i][/u] [URL=http://img94.imageshack.us/i/64645908.png/][IMG]http://img94.imageshack.us/img94/8118/64645908.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img202.imageshack.us/i/93898129.png/][IMG]http://img202.imageshack.us/img202/8622/93898129.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img63.imageshack.us/i/98287696.png/][IMG]http://img63.imageshack.us/img63/2606/98287696.png[/img][/URL] [IMG]http://img196.imageshack.us/img196/73/31070159.png[/img] [URL=http://img43.imageshack.us/i/39887772.png/][IMG]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/1300/39887772.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img20.imageshack.us/i/48502570.png/][IMG]http://img20.imageshack.us/img20/2118/48502570.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img685.imageshack.us/i/77066912.png/][IMG]http://img685.imageshack.us/img685/3530/77066912.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img186.imageshack.us/i/34420132.png/][IMG]http://img186.imageshack.us/img186/5952/34420132.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img214.imageshack.us/i/89839536.png/][IMG]http://img442.imageshack.us/img442/3001/82898962.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img294.imageshack.us/i/16640926.png/][IMG]http://img294.imageshack.us/img294/6118/16640926.png[/img][/URL]
More pictures coming soon!
Please rate, comment, and no flaming please :)
